                        Command: PERIOD

BRIEF DESCRIPTION: This is where all the work is done. On typing this 
command, you will enter the PERIOD_PERIOD sub-menu containing the 
various periodicity finding options. To obtain help on any one of the 
options, simply type HELP 'COMMAND' (eg. HELP SCARGLE).
